  <thing id="pwGuardin1" name="Guardian&apos;s Counter" description="{b}Trigger:{/b} An ally within 2 squares of you is hit by an attack and you are not included in the attack.\n\n{b}Effect:{/b} You and the ally shift up to 2 squares as a free action, swapping positions. You become the target of the triggering attack, in place of the ally. After the attack is resolved, you can make a basic attack against the attacker." compset="Power">
    <fieldval field="pwFlavor" value="Seeing a friend in danger, you step up to take the attack meant for your ally&#151;and then you strike back."/>
    <fieldval field="pwRange1" value="2"/>
